    <item>
      <title>阿达尼港口考虑发行 1.2 亿美元卢比债券，这是 2021 年以来的首次</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-14/adani-ports-mulls-120-million-rupee-bond-sale-first-since-2021</link>
      <description><![CDATA[阿达尼港口和经济特区计划通过私募发行多达 100 亿卢比（1.2 亿美元）的债券，这将是两年来首次发行本币债券。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-14/adani-ports-mulls-120-million-rupee-bond-sale-first-since-2021</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 14 Dec 2023 10:06:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美联储暗示降息 亚洲资产将在 2024 年延续涨势</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-14/asia-assets-set-to-extend-rally-in-2024-as-fed-signals-rate-cuts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在美联储暗示明年可能降息后，亚洲市场掀起了一股欣喜之情，分析师几乎一致呼吁各资产类别继续上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-14/asia-assets-set-to-extend-rally-in-2024-as-fed-signals-rate-cuts</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 14 Dec 2023 09:59:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
