    <item>
      <title>瑞士央行呼吁结束加息周期，标志着瑞郎政策的转变</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-14/snb-rate-on-hold-as-global-pressure-for-rate-cut-pivot-mounts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[瑞士央行宣布结束紧缩周期，并暗示其货币政策将发生转变，在通胀大幅放缓至上限以下后，该行保持借贷成本不变。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-14/snb-rate-on-hold-as-global-pressure-for-rate-cut-pivot-mounts</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 14 Dec 2023 08:40:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美联储鸽派转向后交易员加大全球降息押注</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-14/traders-boost-ecb-and-boe-rate-cut-bets-after-fed-pivot</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着全球市场适应美联储转向宽松政策，交易员在周四晚些时候欧洲央行和英格兰银行做出政策决定之前加大了对全球降息的押注。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-14/traders-boost-ecb-and-boe-rate-cut-bets-after-fed-pivot</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 14 Dec 2023 07:40:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>高盛修改美联储呼吁，认为降息“更早、更快”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-14/goldman-revises-fed-call-now-seeing-earlier-and-faster-cuts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[高盛集团经济学家修改了他们对美联储的展望，认为美联储将从三月份开始稳步降息。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-14/goldman-revises-fed-call-now-seeing-earlier-and-faster-cuts</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 14 Dec 2023 07:01:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国经济停滞令英国央行利率制定者头疼</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-14/where-are-uk-interest-rates-headed-in-2024-bank-of-england-decision-outlook</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国央行周四可能将利率维持在 15 年来的高位，因为人们担心通胀持续存在，同时也有经济可能陷入长期衰退的迹象。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-14/where-are-uk-interest-rates-headed-in-2024-bank-of-england-decision-outlook</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 14 Dec 2023 00:01:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>鸽派美联储因宽松押注刺激股票和债券上涨：市场总结</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-13/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在美联储暗示明年降息后，股市和债券上涨，在通胀压力缓解的乐观情绪中释放了整个市场的看涨脉搏。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-13/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 13 Dec 2023 23:40:36 GMT</pubDate>
